    "5": {
      "title": "Elven Hunter Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Elven_Hunter_Armor_CC\">Elven Hunter Armor <sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Elven&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Elven Hunter Armor CC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Elven Hunter armor is a variant added by the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Elven_Hunter\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Elven Hunter\">Alternative Armors - Elven Hunter</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>. It can be crafted once the quest <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Once_A_Hunter\" title=\"Skyrim:Once A Hunter\">Once A Hunter</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Elven_Hunter\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Elven Hunter\">CC</a></sup> is completed.\n</p><p>The set lacks a helmet and shield, though the regular pieces can be used to get the matching set perk. The set pieces' stats are identical to the regular pieces, except for each piece having two more points in armor rating. As the gilded armor is still superior, it can be combined with the hunter boots and gauntlets, and the regular helmet and shield to get a total armor rating of 89. This combination exceeds the quality of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Scaled_Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Scaled Armor\">scaled armor</a>, while also remaining the lightest armor in the game. In terms of armor rating-to-weight ratio (i.e. the number of armor points per unit of weight), the boots and gauntlets have the highest ratio in the game, tying with the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dark\" title=\"Skyrim:Dark\">Dark</a> equivalents.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/17/SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg/200px-SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/17/SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg/300px-SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/1/17/SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg/400px-SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Elven_Hunter_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A female <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Imperial\" title=\"Skyrim:Imperial\">Imperial</a> wearing elven hunter armor</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"4\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Refined Moonstone.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/87/SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Moonstone.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Refined_Moonstone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Refined Moonstone\">Moonstone</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Iron Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Iron_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Iron Ingot\">Iron</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-Leather.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-Leather.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/9/9b/SR-icon-misc-Leather.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-Leather.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/9/9b/SR-icon-misc-Leather.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-Leather.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/9/9b/SR-icon-misc-Leather.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-Leather.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather\">Leather</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-head