    "6": {
      "title": "Elven Weapons",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Elven_Weapons\">Elven Weapons</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Elven&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Elven Weapons\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Elven weapons are medium-quality weapons that are better than the weapons associated with medium-quality heavy armor, (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dwarven\" title=\"Skyrim:Dwarven\">Dwarven</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Orcish\" title=\"Skyrim:Orcish\">Orcish</a>), but not as good as <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Malachite\" title=\"Skyrim:Malachite\">glass</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ebony\" title=\"Skyrim:Ebony\">ebony</a>. They appear in leveled lists starting at level 19 (enchanted varieties at level 20). All items except ammunition can be <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Grindstone\" title=\"Skyrim:Grindstone\">tempered</a> using one refined moonstone, and having the Elven Smithing perk doubles the quality improvement. Arrows can only be smithed if the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard\">Dawnguard</a> add-on has been installed. Elven Crossbows are only available with the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Elite_Crossbows\" title=\"Skyrim:Elite Crossbows\">Elite Crossbows</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a> installed.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Crit.<br /><a href=\"/wiki/File:SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Damage\"><img alt=\"Damage\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/22px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/33px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/ab/SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png/44px-SkyrimTAG-icon-Heavy_Attack.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Speed\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Reach\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"5\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">D