t-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"#note_Elite\">‡</a></span>This item can only be crafted after completing the quest <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Night_Hunter\" title=\"Skyrim:Night Hunter\">Night Hunter</a></div>\n<div id=\"intnote_Enhanced\" class=\"citation\" style=\"display:flow-root; clear: left; position: relative; margin-left: 1.6em; min-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"position: absolute; right: 100%; margin-right: 0.2em; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"#note_Enhanced\">¥</a></span>The Enhanced Crossbow has an additional property: <i>Attacks with this crossbow ignore 50% of armor.</i></div>\n<p><sup>†</sup> The base gold value used for all <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Generic_Magic_Weapons\" title=\"Skyrim:Generic Magic Weapons\">generic enchanted</a> versions of the elven bow is 165 instead of 470. This means that the enchanted weapons are 305 gold cheaper than they should be, and in several cases are cheaper than the unenchanted bow. This bug is shared by several types of bow in the game.</p><ul><li> <img alt=\"PC Only\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/d/d7/Computer.svg\" title=\"PC Only\" width=\"21\" height=\"22\" /> The <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim_Mod:Unofficial_Skyrim_Patch\" title=\"Skyrim Mod:Unofficial Skyrim Patch\">Unofficial Skyrim Patch</a>, version 1.3.1, fixes this bug. </li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content3.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152056\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.045 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.105 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2547/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9812/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2823/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 358/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   41.148      1 -total\n 16.70%    6.870     15 Template:Icon\n 15.14%    6.229      3 Template:Weight_Ic